861
00:48:57,920 --> 00:49:01,440
他做了不该做的事，但我不能把他钉在十字架上。
he did something he shouldn't have, but I can't crucify him.

862
00:49:03,560 --> 00:49:06,880
加里很棒。多可爱的人啊。我们有多幸运?
And Gary's great. What a lovely man. How lucky are we?

863
00:49:10,080 --> 00:49:11,820
