868
00:49:32,640 --> 00:49:35,940
所以你也没给你爸发短信吗?
Is that why you didn't text your dad either?

869
00:49:37,040 --> 00:49:41,640
如果这能安慰你的话。我觉得你很完美。
Well, if it's any consolation. I think you're perfect.

870
00:49:48,600 --> 00:49:50,630
我最好给他打个电话。
I'd better ring him.

871
00:49:50,680 --> 00:49:52,550
看看他想要什么。
See what he wants.

872
00:50:02,400 --> 00:50:04,270
~迟了!对不起。~没关系。
~ Late! Sorry. ~ That's OK.

873
00:50:04,320 --> 00:50:05,830
你好吗？
How are you?

874
00:50:05,880 --> 00:50:07,880
我能喝点茶吗?
Can I have some tea?

875
00:50:09,560 --> 00:50:12,150
谢谢你来见我。很高兴见到你。
~ Thanks for meeting me. ~ It's nice to see you.

876
00:50:12,200 --> 00:50:14,030
是吗?
Is it?

877
00:50:14,080 --> 00:50:16,480
为什么不呢?~嗯…
~ Why wouldn't it be? ~ Well...

878
00:50:17,000 --> 00:50:18,470
艾伦已经两周没给我打电话了。
Alan hasn't rung me for two weeks.

879
00:50:18,520 --> 00:50:20,510
他一直在哈罗盖特。~是的。
~ He's been in Harrogate. ~ Yeah.

880
00:50:20,560 --> 00:50:24,950
这一切都很痛苦。适合所有人。
It's all been pretty traumatic. For everyone.

881
00:50:25,000 --> 00:50:28,360
确定。但你也没给我打电话。直到星期天。
Sure. But then you didn't ring me either. Till Sunday.

882
00:50:31,000 --> 00:50:33,670
嗯，我也有点忙不过来了。
Well, I've been a bit snowed under meself as well.

883
00:50:33,720 --> 00:50:36,510
课程。课程。我只是有点多疑。
Course. Course. It's just that I'm paranoid.

884
00:50:36,560 --> 00:50:38,700
是吗?~不正常。
~ Are you? ~ Not normally.

885
00:50:41,800 --> 00:50:43,510
拉夫怎么样了?
How's Raff doing?

886
00:50:43,560 --> 00:50:47,590
很好!他很喜欢。他很棒，是个很好的小伙子。
Really well! He loves it. He's great, he's such a nice lad.

887
00:50:47,640 --> 00:50:48,950
谢谢你！他可以。
Thank you. He can be.

888
00:50:49,000 --> 00:50:52,200
当他不是…自大的小混蛋。
When he's not being a... cocky little dick.

889
00:50:55,760 --> 00:50:58,510
我和费利西蒂最近关系不太好。
Me and Felicity haven't been getting on very well lately.

890
00:50:58,560 --> 00:51:00,870
~真的吗?~对不起，那是……
~ Really? ~ Sorry, that's...

891
00:51:00,920 --> 00:51:03,430
~没有。~我是说…自从这一切发生之后。
~ No. ~ I mean... it's since all this.

892
00:51:03,480 --> 00:51:05,870
所以可能都是我的错。
So it's probably all my fault.

893
00:51:05,920 --> 00:51:07,990
为什么?你是什么意思?
Why? What do you mean?

894
00:51:09,280 --> 00:51:10,590
我突然……
I suddenly...

895
00:51:10,640 --> 00:51:12,510
我感到很生气。
I felt very angry.

896
00:51:13,920 --> 00:51:16,630
那个星期天我们一起吃过午饭之后。
After we'd been over for lunch the other Sunday.

897
00:51:16,680 --> 00:51:18,230
为什么?
Why?

898
00:51:18,280 --> 00:51:20,020
卡洛琳怎么样?
How's Caroline?

899
00:51:21,120 --> 00:51:24,070
她的应对。你为什么生气?
She's coping. Why did you feel angry?

900
00:51:24,120 --> 00:51:25,990
我不知道为什么。
I don't know why.

901
00:51:26,920 --> 00:51:28,470
~这不是…对…生气?
~ It's not... ~ Angry with...?

902
00:51:28,520 --> 00:51:33,070
一切。与…为什么我的父母从来不告诉我。
Everything. With... Why my parents never told me.

903
00:51:33,120 --> 00:51:36,070
你知道，我现在再也不能和他们谈这个话题了。
You know, that's a conversation that I can never have with them now.

904
00:51:36,120 --> 00:51:38,510
是的，我知道。我明白了。我明白。
Yeah, I know. I understand. I do understand.

905
00:51:38,560 --> 00:51:39,950
因为我对……
Because I feel the same about...

906
00:51:40,000 --> 00:51:42,790
我记起了一些事情。过去发生的事情。
And I'm remembering things. Things that happened in the past.

907
00:51:42,840 --> 00:51:47,350
我想知道他们是否更关心我们的亚当——我的兄弟——而不是我。
And I'm wondering whether they did think more about our Adam - my brother - than they did about me.

908
00:51:47,400 --> 00:51:50,790
~他比呃…年轻?~是啊!我爸爸是他爸爸，他真正的爸爸。
~ He's younger than erm...? ~ Yeah! Yeah, and my dad was his dad, his proper dad.

909
00:51:50,840 --> 00:51:55,190
我从来没有，从来没有这样想过。
And I've never, NEVER thought like this before.

910
00:51:55,240 --> 00:52:00,870
我以前从来没有生气或嫉妒过。好吧，不是这样的。
I've never felt angry or jealous before. Well, not like this.

911
00:52:00,920 --> 00:52:02,670
我知道。
I know.

912
00:52:02,720 --> 00:52:06,190
它改变了过去。几乎。尽管事实并非如此。
It changes the past. Almost. Even though it doesn't.

913
00:52:06,240 --> 00:52:11,750
但是，是的。它给过去涂上了色彩。是的，这很难。
But it - yeah. It colours the past. And yeah, that's difficult.

914
00:52:11,800 --> 00:52:13,830
~但是…~那就没人…没人给我打电话。
~ But... ~ Then no-one... nobody rings me up.

915
00:52:13,880 --> 00:52:15,270
在那个星期天之后，
After that Sunday,

916
00:52:15,320 --> 00:52:17,710
所以我脑子里满是关于我亲生父母的事
so I've got all this shit in my head about my real parents,

917
00:52:17,760 --> 00:52:21,190
我在想，“哦，现在他真的不想了解我了”。
and I'm thinking, "Oh, and now he doesn't really want to get to know me".

918
00:52:21,240 --> 00:52:24,710
~不，那是……但是我总是要打电话。
~ No, that's... ~ But I am the one who always has to do the ringing up.

919
00:52:24,760 --> 00:52:28,630
不。加里。诚实。你想得太多了。
No. Gary. Honestly. You're reading too much into it.

920
00:52:28,680 --> 00:52:30,110
这几周很奇怪。
It's been an odd few weeks.

921
00:52:30,160 --> 00:52:32,300
你要结婚了!
You're getting married!

922
00:52:33,400 --> 00:52:34,670
是啊!
Yeah!

923
00:52:35,800 --> 00:52:37,230
你被邀请了!
You are invited!

924
00:52:37,280 --> 00:52:38,620
真的吗?
Really?

925
00:52:39,440 --> 00:52:42,910
如果你担心没有我爸爸的消息，就给他打电话!
Just ring me dad up if you're worried you've not heard from him!

926
00:52:42,960 --> 00:52:46,070
~是的，但是我…~什么?我不敢。
~ Yeah, but I... ~ What? ~ I daren't.

927
00:52:46,120 --> 00:52:48,870
不敢吗?你是加里·杰克逊!
Daren't? You're Gary Jackson!

928
00:52:48,920 --> 00:52:50,870
那不代表什么!
That doesn't mean anything!

929
00:52:50,920 --> 00:52:54,030
我可不想最后总觉得自己是个讨厌鬼!
I don't want to end up feeling like I'm being a nuisance all the time!

930
00:52:54,080 --> 00:52:56,820
我爸爸不会那样想的。
My dad would never think like that.

931
00:52:57,480 --> 00:52:58,950
你的爸爸?
Your dad?

932
00:53:00,160 --> 00:53:03,590
是的。我爸爸，你爸爸。无论什么。
Yeah. My dad, your dad. Whatever.

933
00:53:03,640 --> 00:53:05,030
他对我感兴趣，是吗?
He is interested in me, isn't he?

934
00:53:05,080 --> 00:53:08,070
是的!绝对的!他觉得你很棒!
Yes! Absolutely! He thinks you're fantastic!

935
00:53:08,120 --> 00:53:10,270
西莉亚也喜欢我。
And Celia liked me.

936
00:53:10,320 --> 00:53:13,230
她爱你。~对不起。
~ She loved you. ~ Sorry.

937
00:53:13,280 --> 00:53:15,790
~不要…~我不是这样的。这，这只是…
~ Don't... ~ I'm not like this. This - it's just...

938
00:53:15,840 --> 00:53:20,430
真是太震惊了，吉莉安。和…这就像……
it's just been such a shock, Gillian. And... It's like...

939
00:53:20,480 --> 00:53:22,710
我才刚刚明白过来。正常。所有的…
it's only just sunk in. Properly. All the...

940
00:53:22,760 --> 00:53:25,870
~我知道。~影响。~我知道。我知道。
~ I know. ~ Implications. ~ I know. I do know.

941
00:53:25,920 --> 00:53:28,870
对不起。我——对不起——我被迷住了。
Sorry. I get - sorry - I get obsessed.

942
00:53:28,920 --> 00:53:32,720
还有一些奇怪的事情。这就是我!
And a little bit weird about stuff. That's just me!

943
00:53:35,600 --> 00:53:38,790
她给我端茶来了吗?~冷静点。
~ Is she even bringing me some tea? ~ Calm down.

944
00:53:38,840 --> 00:53:41,580
~是的。是的。是的。是的。~冷静点。
~ Yeah. Yeah. Yeah. Yeah. ~ Calm down.

945
00:53:55,920 --> 00:53:58,070
我一到家就给你发邮件。
I'm going to e-mail you the second I'm home.

946
00:53:58,120 --> 00:53:59,550
是的。请做。
Yes. Please do.

947
00:53:59,600 --> 00:54:02,150
我要回来过暑假。~好。
~ And I'm going to be back for the summer. ~ Good.

948
00:54:02,200 --> 00:54:05,430
整整两个星期!
For two whole weeks!

949
00:54:05,480 --> 00:54:08,480
我要给你带很多东西!
And I'm going to bring you so much stuff!

950
00:54:10,080 --> 00:54:12,680
然后你和妈妈
And then you and Mom -

951
00:54:13,760 --> 00:54:16,590
这个妈妈要来看我。
this Mom - are going to visit me.

952
00:54:16,640 --> 00:54:18,710
~是的。~没错。
~ We are. ~ That's right.

953
00:54:20,200 --> 00:54:21,680
西莉亚。
Celia.

954
00:54:23,360 --> 00:54:25,710
祝你一路平安。
You have a safe journey.

955
00:54:25,760 --> 00:54:27,030
艾伦。
Alan.

956
00:54:30,040 --> 00:54:32,110
你们俩真是太好了。
You've both been so kind.

957
00:54:32,160 --> 00:54:35,390
你们保持联系。我们两个，还有这两个。
You keep in touch. With us two, as well as these two.

958
00:54:35,440 --> 00:54:37,880
我会的，我当然会。
I will, of course I will.

959
00:55:10,760 --> 00:55:13,520
你还好吧，亲爱的?~是的。
~ Y'all right, love? ~ Yup.

960
00:55:23,160 --> 00:55:25,070
艾略特博士吗?
Dr Elliot?

961
00:55:25,120 --> 00:55:26,870
霍莉?
Holly?

962
00:55:26,920 --> 00:55:29,670
这是…吗?这里是康威路46号。
Is this...? This is 46 Conway Drive.

963
00:55:29,720 --> 00:55:31,510
我在找麦肯齐-道森医生。
I'm looking for a Dr McKenzie-Dawson.

964
00:55:31,560 --> 00:55:34,110
~哦。是的。那就是我。~是吗?
~ Oh. Yes. That's me. ~ Is it?

965
00:55:34,160 --> 00:55:36,430
是的……我，我结婚了。
Yes... I - I got married.

966
00:55:37,640 --> 00:55:41,390
天啊。好。中介派我来的。
Gosh. Well. The agency sent me.

967
00:55:41,440 --> 00:55:45,230
我早到了十分钟，不过如果你愿意，我可以先走了再回来。~不，不，不要那样做。
~ And I'm ten minutes early, but I can go away and come back if you like. ~ No, no, don't do that.

968
00:55:45,280 --> 00:55:48,750
~但是…你去苏塞克斯读社会学。~我退学了!
~ But... you went off to Sussex to read sociology. ~ I dropped out!

969
00:55:48,800 --> 00:55:50,990
那个姓，当中介打来电话的时候……那不是……
The surname - when the agency rang... That wasn't...

970
00:55:51,040 --> 00:55:53,470
~我没有…~我退学了，我也结婚了!
~ I didn't... ~ I dropped out and I got married too!

971
00:55:53,520 --> 00:55:55,670
现在我是保姆了。我从没想过去苏塞克斯。
And now I'm a nanny. I never wanted to go to Sussex.

972
00:55:55,720 --> 00:55:58,270
是我的父母。祝福他们。和你!
It was my parents. Bless them. And you!

973
00:55:58,320 --> 00:56:00,070
对我们所有人来说都是如此雄心勃勃!
So ambitious for us all!

974
00:56:00,120 --> 00:56:03,470
但我真正想做的就是这个。这就是我要做的!
But all I ever really wanted to do was this. And now that's what I am doing!

975
00:56:03,520 --> 00:56:06,710
老实说，我再高兴不过了。
And I couldn't be happier, honestly.

976
00:56:06,760 --> 00:56:09,990
冬青。这是我妈妈。这是我的继父。
Holly. This is my mother. And this is my stepfather.

977
00:56:10,040 --> 00:56:12,350
你好!~西莉亚。
~ How do you do? ~ Celia.

978
00:56:12,400 --> 00:56:14,270
艾伦。你好。
Alan. Hello.

979
00:56:14,320 --> 00:56:16,390
这是弗洛拉。
And this is Flora.

980
00:56:16,440 --> 00:56:20,470
你好,植物!我的天哪，你真漂亮!
Hello, Flora! My goodness me, aren't you pretty?

981
00:56:20,520 --> 00:56:22,270
多漂亮的皮肤啊。
What beautiful skin.

982
00:56:22,320 --> 00:56:23,990
我不是她的生母。
I'm not her biological mother.

983
00:56:24,040 --> 00:56:27,630
做的,嗯…局里跟你解释过我的情况了吗?
Did, erm... did the agency explain my situation to you?

984
00:56:27,680 --> 00:56:29,920
不。不，不完全是。
No. Not - not entirely.

985
00:56:31,560 --> 00:56:33,110
你想喝点茶吗?
Would you like some tea?

986
00:56:33,160 --> 00:56:34,870
我想喝点茶。
I'd love some tea.

987
00:56:34,920 --> 00:56:37,470
~你想进来吗?~谢谢。
~ Do you want to come inside? ~ Thank you.

988
00:56:37,520 --> 00:56:39,470
多漂亮的房子啊!
What a gorgeous house!

989
00:56:39,520 --> 00:56:41,230
天哪，看看这些虹膜。
Gosh, look at those irises.

990
00:56:41,280 --> 00:56:43,590
那绝对是我最喜欢的颜色。
That's my absolute number one favourite colour.

991
00:56:43,640 --> 00:56:45,990
哇。那是你的车吗?
Wow. Is that your car?

992
00:56:46,040 --> 00:56:47,390
不,这是……
No, it's...

993
00:56:47,440 --> 00:56:48,710
真的吗?好样的!
Really? Good for you!

994
00:56:48,760 --> 00:56:51,590
如果我可以选择一辆车，我想我会选那辆。认真对待。
If I could choose a car, I think I'd choose that one. Seriously.

995
00:56:51,640 --> 00:56:54,880
除了我不敢开它。我想我还是看着它吧。
Except I'd be scared to drive it. I think I'd just rather look at it.

996
00:56:55,840 --> 00:56:58,240
天啊，这走廊真漂亮……
Gosh, it's a nice hallway...

997
00:56:59,640 --> 00:57:01,590
今天我们可能会去克纳斯伯勒野餐。
Today we might take a picnic to Knaresborough.

998
00:57:01,640 --> 00:57:04,230
我们刚接到布拉德福德警方的电话。
We've just had a phone call from the police in Bradford.

999
00:57:04,280 --> 00:57:06,750
~他们抓走了弗洛拉。警察抓了弗洛拉?
~ They've got Flora. ~ The police've got Flora?

1000
00:57:06,800 --> 00:57:08,230
我告诉过你我不想要孩子。
I told you I didn't want a baby.

1001
00:57:08,280 --> 00:57:09,630
我说过我不想要孩子。
I said I didn't want a baby.

1002
00:57:09,680 --> 00:57:12,870
我在撒谎。说我从没告诉过任何人。
I'm lying. Saying I never told anyone.

1003
00:57:12,920 --> 00:57:14,990
劳伦斯，这是格雷格。~你好。
~ Lawrence, this is Greg. ~ Hi.

1004
00:57:15,040 --> 00:57:16,470
再见。
Bye.

1005
00:57:16,520 --> 00:57:18,550
凯特去世还不到六周。
It's less than six weeks since Kate died.

1006
00:57:18,600 --> 00:57:21,150
~好。你真的在问我这个问题吗?
~ Well. ~ Are you seriously asking me that question?

1007
00:57:21,200 --> 00:57:24,040
还有一件事……你会误解我的意思的。
Then the other thing... Oh, you're going to take this the wrong way.

